b862352f-9c70-4387-98cb-ff049f3ffd1a.title: <player>
b862352f-9c70-4387-98cb-ff049f3ffd1a.text:
Hello. I have some fine silk from far away to sell to
you.

9beab3fe-b674-4b60-baff-9db12f538884.title: Silk merchant
9beab3fe-b674-4b60-baff-9db12f538884.text:
Ah I may be interested in that. What sort of price were
you looking at per piece of silk?

fdf905e5-9c9b-4ade-989d-1018f6d8a8df.title: Silk merchant
fdf905e5-9c9b-4ade-989d-1018f6d8a8df.text:
I buy silk. If you ever want to
sell any silk, bring it here.

04ac44be-a652-41b7-8bbe-4410a0038cb2.title: Silk merchant
04ac44be-a652-41b7-8bbe-4410a0038cb2.text:
80 coins? That's a bit steep!
How about 40 coins?

f9be5a2d-a0ee-47d5-8945-f9568116636f.title: Silk merchant
f9be5a2d-a0ee-47d5-8945-f9568116636f.text:
You'll never get that much for it. I'll be generous and
give you 50 for it.

options.text: I'll give it to you for 60.

cea5ecca-e059-413b-b3d7-db6d5fc8c35e.title: <player>
cea5ecca-e059-413b-b3d7-db6d5fc8c35e.text: I'll give it to you for 60.

7a14d413-eb4a-4644-81c2-dc0e2169412d.title: Silk merchant
7a14d413-eb4a-4644-81c2-dc0e2169412d.text:
You drive a hard bargain, but
I guess that will have to do.

dace56b5-fcb5-437e-a028-04e335b833c2.title: Silk merchant
dace56b5-fcb5-437e-a028-04e335b833c2.text:
Don't be ridiculous! That is far too much. You insult
me with that price.
